* Oral history interview with Stephen Wampler, Charles Babbage Institute, University of Minnesota. Wampler discusses his work on the development of the Icon programming language in the late 1970s at the University of Arizona under Ralph Griswold.
* Oral history interview with Robert Goldberg, Charles Babbage Institute, University of Minnesota. Goldberg discusses his interaction with Ralph Griswold when working on the Icon programming language.
* Charles Hall Collection on the SNOBOL Programming Language at the Charles Babbage Institute, University of Minnesota.
