<doc id="793112" wikidata="Q3396130" url="?curid=793112" title="Ponary">
<text>Ponary is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Miłakowo, within Ostróda County, Warmian-Masurian Voivodeship, in northern Poland. It lies approximately south of Miłakowo, north of Ostróda, and north-west of the regional capital Olsztyn.

