* &quot;Pimlico&quot; / &quot;This is For Real&quot; // &quot;Magic Life&quot; / &quot;David&#x27;s Coming Back&quot; – Sept 1996
* &quot;Miscellaneous&quot; / &quot;Ballroom&quot; – 1996
