<doc id="793420" wikidata="Q715995" url="?curid=793420" title="Taylor Ball">
<text>Taylor Ball (born December 28, 1987) is an American musician and former actor known for his portrayal of Brian Miller in the television sitcom &quot;Still Standing&quot; and Eddie in Disney&#x27;s &quot;Eddie&#x27;s Million Dollar Cook-Off&quot;. Ball has also appeared on &quot;Walker, Texas Ranger&quot;. Since 2017, he has been in the band “Tragic Forms”.

